OL,3,CFamily pay tributes to 'Bubbly' 6-year-
OL,4,Cold after fatal collision
OL,6,FThe family of a six-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fdied following a collision in
OL,8,FEllesmere Port have paid tribute to
OL,9,Ftheir "beautiful, bubbly" son, saying
OL,10,Fhe "brought so much joy" to everyone
OL,11,Fwho knew him.
OL,13,FKanan-Jay McLeod died on Sunday 19
OL,14,FApril, after he was struck by a black
OL,15,FInfiniti FX30D car on Anchor Drive in
OL,16,FEllesmere Port, Cheshire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
