CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778217983
OL,3,CFamily pay tributes to 'Bubbly' 6-year-
OL,4,Cold after fatal collision
OL,6,FEmergency services treated Kanan-Jay
OL,7,Fnear Whitby Sports and Social Club
OL,8,Fbefore he was taken to the Countess of
OL,9,FChester Hospital, but he died from his
OL,10,Finjuries.
OL,12,FIn a statement, Kanan-Jay's family
OL,13,Fsaid: "Our beautiful, bubbly little
OL,14,Fboy Kanan-Jay brought so much joy to
OL,15,Feveryone who knew him.
OL,17,F"He was a cheeky little character with
OL,18,Fa big smile, a kind heart and an
OL,19,Finfectious personality, with a love
OL,20,Ffor gaming, cars and football,
OL,21,Fespecially Liverpool Football Club.
OL,26,@uD@GOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778217983
OL,3,CFamily pay tributes to 'Bubbly' 6-year-
OL,4,Cold after fatal collision
OL,6,F"He adored spending time playing with
OL,7,Fhis cousins, his friends, his auntie T
OL,8,Fand uncles Lewis and Liam, filling our
OL,9,Fdays with happy memories that we will
OL,10,Ftreasure forever.
OL,12,F"As a family, we are heartbroken, but
OL,13,Fwe are also incredibly grateful for
OL,14,Fthe kindness, love and support shown
OL,15,Fto us by the community during this
OL,16,Funimaginable time. Thank you for
OL,17,Fhelping us honour our Kanan-Jay."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
