CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778217983
OL,3,CFamily pay tributes to 'Bubbly' 6-year-
OL,4,Cold after fatal collision
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Iain Condliffe
OL,7,Fsaid: "This was a tragic incident in
OL,8,Fwhich a young child lost his life, and
OL,9,Fwe are committed to doing all we can
OL,10,Fto establish exactly what took place.
OL,12,F"We urge anyone who witnessed the
OL,13,Finitial collision on Anchor Drive, or
OL,14,Fwho has any video footage or was
OL,15,Fpresent when the child was treated
OL,16,Fnear Whitby Sports and Social Club, to
OL,17,Fcome forward."
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOUyD@NO]
