OL,3,CFamily pay tributes to 'Bubbly' 6-year-
OL,4,Cold after fatal collision
OL,6,FPolice confirmed that a 48-year-old
OL,7,Fman was arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fcausing death by dangerous driving,
OL,9,Fdrug driving and driving without a
OL,10,Flicence.
OL,12,FHe has since been bailed pending
OL,13,Ffurther inquiries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
